text: Frenchville FC is a football club based in Rockhampton, Queensland. The club was established in 1948. They competed in the 1979 and 1980 Queensland State League seasons. They currently compete in the Central Queensland Premier League. ==External links== * Official club website == References == Category:Soccer clubs in Queensland Category:Association football clubs established in 1948 Category:1948 establishments in Australia
